title: Franklin D. Roosevelt Metro Station
description: Serving Lines 1 and 9, this is the oldest Metro station in Paris. It was originally called Marbeuf-Rond Point Des Champs Elysees and was renamed in honour of the American President in 1946.

title: Adele's Video Film Location (Someone Like You)
description: This is the location where Adele's video was filmed.  She walks west and then turns south.  With Google's Street View you can pan 360° at the corner and see all of the buildings in the video (Eiffel Tower).
